quests.name: Starry Skies
quests.description: In the Starry Skies dimension you can get many resourches. But first, you have to collect some resources in the Aether. Just mine Zenite Ore and kill a Blue Swet. Use Zenite Blocks as the Portal frame and ignite it with a Swet Ball.

quests.name: Sky Islands
quests.description: In this Dimension you can dicover many biomes and strutures. The Portal frame has to be build out of Mossy Glowshroom Caps. To ignite it, right click with a Amethyst Shard.

quests.name: Sky End
quests.description: In this modpack you can discover two end dimensions. Travel around in the Starry Skies Dimension and search for a large sphere made out of Stone Bricks. Inside it you will find a End Portal.

quests.name: Sky Nether
quests.description: This is a other kind of an Void Nether, it is filled with a lot of spheres. Just build a Nether Portal in the Starry Skies Dimension to reach it.

quests.name: The Aether
quests.description: Travel to the Aether by forming a Portal out of Glowstone Blocks. Ignite it with a Bucket of Water.

quests.name: Space Travel Preparations
quests.description: If you want to go into space, you have to prepare. Start by melting some dirt into oxide.

quests.name: Moon
quests.description: Continue your preparations and follow the directions in the Space Explorer's Guide. Then you should be able to travel to the moon soon. Explore the other celestial bodies as well.

quests.name: The End
quests.description: In the Sky Islands Dimension you can search for a end stronghold.

quests.name: The Bumblezone
quests.description: Throw an Ender Pearl on a bee's nest / hive to get into the dimension. Exit the dimension by digging up to Y=256. Maybe travel back to your island with the Glider.
